General,Motors,has,created,an,API,accessible,application,development,platform,for,their,vehicles,This,platform,is,accessible,through,an,in,vehicle,API,and,a,remote,API,The,GM,Remote,API,scheduled,to,be,available,late,in,supports,development,of,applications,that,remotely,interact,with,GM,vehicles,Supported,methods,include,vehicle,commands,such,as,unlocking,doors,or,activating,the,alarm,and,accessing,subscriber,or,vehicle,data